channel.title: Authors & Contributors :: K-State Computational Core
channel.description: Note This curriculum was developed at Kansas State University with the help of many authors, each with unique contributions to the material. This page lists all attributed authors and contributors, as well as links to their respective pages if available. We hope to have everyone who has been a part of this project listed on this page. If you have contributed and are not listed here, please contact us at csoffice@ksu.
